Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:17.45,title3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(523,290)}骨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂初佳今天的任务是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送达大小姐忘带的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美无瑕的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  别看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破绽！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务总是伴随着意外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过特别训练的我是绝不会因此动摇的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动要迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不拖泥带水  保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没看到关键部位  完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成后就马上告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别在意保持原状保持…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原状？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女仆的任务十分艰巨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  上帝有时也会给点奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.71,0:23:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的总结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:55.83,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)}人生有苦也有甜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣忘送了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待续
